Ask HN: SF AGI/Alignment/WTF-Is-Happening Meetups
text:
Anyone know of any SF AI meetups? Seems like AGI/Alignment is a hot topic and would be interesting to get some discussions going.

I imagine we've got a city full of people interested/scared/motivated to think deeply about this and that maybe/possibly (if there's any optimism to be spared) could do something about it.

Does anything like this exist already? If not, anyone down?
